*SHOW Reorder the characters (using Delfor - cannot be used with Confor).

*LISTING FILE reorder.lst

*COMMENT This directives file cannot be used with CONFOR.

*INPUT FILE specs
*COMMENT This statement was not required for the original DELFOR
*INPUT FILE items

*OUTPUT WIDTH 80

*COMMENT Move character 85 ('number of species') to 2.
*NEW CHARACTER ORDER 1 85 2-84 86-89

*COMMENT This statement is no longer required.
*INPUT DELTA FILE confor.cph

*COMMENT. CONFOR files.
*REFORMAT specs
*REFORMAT chars
*REFORMAT items
*REFORMAT cimages
*REFORMAT cnotes
*REFORMAT empchari
*REFORMAT empcharm
*REFORMAT headc
*REFORMAT layout
*REFORMAT summary
*REFORMAT toali
*REFORMAT todis
*REFORMAT tohen
*REFORMAT toint
*REFORMAT tokey
*REFORMAT tonex
*REFORMAT topau
*REFORMAT topay

*COMMENT. KEY files.
*REFORMAT key4
*REFORMAT key6

*COMMENT This statement is no longer required.
*INPUT DELTA FILE intkey.cph

*COMMENT. INTKEY files.
*REFORMAT intkey.ini
